  "title": "MNC Lab Technician / Chemical Technician / Entry level /Junior 5Days",
  "description": "<p><strong>Entry level / Junior welcome apply</strong></p>\n<p><strong>5 days work week / Permanent Role / Company transport provided</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Full training provided !!</strong></p>\n<p>Job Responsibilities :<br>\n* Perform quality control analysis for in-coming, intermediate and final products<br>\n* Carry out calibration of equipment and ensure in working condition<br>\n* Ensure activities in the laboratory are safe<br>\n* Maintain up to date analysis reports</p>\n<p>Job Requirements :<br>\n* Nitec / Diploma in Chemical Process Technology / Chemistry or equivalent<br>\n* Preferably with hand on experience in sampling, preparation and analysis for<br>\nliquid samples<br>\n* Prefer experience in handling laboratory analytical<br>\nequipment</p>\n<p>Good Pay + Good allowance + Good Bonus</p>\n<p>Interested candidates please send an updated Resume / CV  in Ms Word format to lilian@recruitflash.com or WhatsApp’s your resume to 98332779 ( no Calls)</p>\n<p>Consultant in-charge : Quah Li Lian (Lilian) ( Registration No: R1983286 )</p>",
